0.name: FRANCE AUTHENTIC JERSEY 2018
0.description: Identical to the game shirt worn by Argentina's superstars at the 2018 FIFA World Cup Russia™, this jersey delivers every possible on-field advantage. It's a modern interpretation of an away shirt that stayed in the kit bag during the team's dominance of South America in the early '90s. Made of smooth, lightweight fabric that dries quickly and keeps you super cool, this premium jersey is built to perform at the highest level.
